name: Emily Naso
coverLetter: I always have been in love with Cannabis. Ever since I was young, I've been trying to get my hands on the newest stuff. I started trimming about 6 years ago. I always had friends that grow and they always needed help trimming. I have trimmed ounces at a time. It has been one of my hobbies my whole life and always will be. Thank you very much for your consideration.
